_description: Quid est homo? — six rhyming lines

UnivLon657.Transcription:
Dethys abydyngA pylgrym pasyngA gest witowtyn dwellyngMan
                    ys dethys vnderlyngMan is a gest in hys dwellyngMan is a pylgrym in
                    his pasyng
UnivLon657.Note:
This item should perhaps be renumbered according to the first three
                    lines, seemingly an abbreviated and anticipatory version of the last
                    three.
